    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "*\nProf. S. P.\nMa Heng, the Director General\nof the National\nPalace Museum, Peiping,\nrequests\nthe\npleasure of your company\nat\nreception\nin nonour or\nthe\nMembers\nof\nthe\nEconomic Mission\nEx-Imperial\nGarden\non\nMonday\nafternoon,\nMay\nthe Thirteenth\nfrom\no'clock.\nVisit to exhibition\nrooms from three\nto five o'clock.\nTea and refreshments from\nfive to six o'clock.\nEntrance through\nShen Wu Men\nopposite\nCoal Hill.",
      "Mrs. H. M. Bixby,\nPeking Hotel,\nPelping."
    ],
